works.description: After I came across the beautiful mahogany bikes by Sueshiro SANO, I have kinda started liking the wooden bicycles, as they are not just bikes but true works of art or perfect furniture pieces to ride on. But, nothing we have seen so far matches the splendor of the SplinterBike, which has its every part made from wood, be it the wheels, frame, gears or the saddle. There is no metal, plastic or rubber; everything on the SplinterBike is wooden.
